ome of the most challenging and varied puzzles by building weird and wacky lollipops.<br><br>• DISCOVER different contraptions and confectionery that will put your puzzle-solving skills to the test. These Pops are no child’s play!<br><br>• UNLOCK puzzle sets and progress from Trainee to Sweet Savant. Can you complete all the Puzzlepops?",
